<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:11:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国风机制造商参与欧盟项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-wind-turbine-makers-involvement-eu-projects-2024-04-10/</link><description>欧盟委员会已要求提供信息，作为对中国风力涡轮机制造商在五个欧盟国家可能存在的市场扭曲进行初步审查的一部分，中国称此举具有“歧视性”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-wind-turbine-makers-involvement-eu-projects-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>政府通知称美国限制与俄罗斯、中国、阿联酋 11 个实体的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-restricts-trade-with-11-entities-russia-china-uae-government-notice-says-2024-04-10/</link><description>据联邦政府称，美国商务部周三将来自俄罗斯、中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国的 11 个实体列入政府出口管制名单，原因是它们违反了伊朗制裁、乌克兰战争和中东油轮袭击等相关规定。发帖。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-restricts-trade-with-11-entities-russia-china-uae-government-notice-says-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔将房地产巨头万科的信用评级下调至垃圾级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sp-slashes-property-giant-china-vankes-credit-rating-junk-2024-04-10/</link><description>周三，对于遭受重创的中国房地产行业来说，还有更多坏消息，标普全球成为最后一家取消万科投资级别的主要信用评级公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sp-slashes-property-giant-china-vankes-credit-rating-junk-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织警告产业政策并不是解决经济增长缓慢的灵丹妙药</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-warns-industrial-policy-no-magic-cure-slow-economic-growth-2024-04-10/</link><description>国际货币基金组织周三表示，美国、欧洲和其他国家最近为引导某些行业的创新而采取的产业政策举措并不是促进经济增长的灵丹妙药。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:04:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-warns-industrial-policy-no-magic-cure-slow-economic-growth-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织称全球贸易在2023年罕见下滑后将稳步复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-trade-recover-steadily-after-rare-fall-2023-wto-says-2024-04-10/</link><description>世界贸易组织周三表示，今年全球货物贸易应该会反弹，但速度会比之前预期的要慢，在 2023 年，全球货物贸易将出现 30 年来的第三次下滑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-trade-recover-steadily-after-rare-fall-2023-wto-says-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>高盛上调中国2024年经济增长预期至5.0%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/goldman-sachs-lifts-china-2024-growth-forecast-50-2024-04-10/</link><description>高盛周三在一份报告中表示，由于中国制造业实力强劲，高盛上调了对中国一季度和2024年全年经济同比增长的预测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/goldman-sachs-lifts-china-2024-growth-forecast-50-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>Cucinelli 董事长表示第一季度表现强劲，包括在中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cucinelli-chairman-flags-strong-first-quarter-including-china-2024-04-10/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团 Brunello Cucinelli 创始人兼执行董事长周三表示，该集团第一季度表现良好，包括在美国和中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cucinelli-chairman-flags-strong-first-quarter-including-china-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis首席执行官表示，在意大利的中国汽车制造可能会迫使他们做出艰难的决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-extend-production-ice-fiat-panda-city-car-2030-ceo-days-2024-04-10/</link><description>意大利唯一的主要汽车制造商法意集团负责人周三表示，在意大利的中国汽车制造可能会迫使 Stellantis 做出一些艰难的决定，包括关闭工厂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-extend-production-ice-fiat-panda-city-car-2030-ceo-days-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将针对中国扭曲的贸易指导延伸至新领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-extends-trade-guide-chinese-distortions-new-sectors-2024-04-10/</link><description>欧盟委员会更新了关于国家主导的中国经济扭曲的报告，增加了新的行业，并可能为欧盟芯片和清洁技术生产商的反倾销投诉打开大门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:49:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-extends-trade-guide-chinese-distortions-new-sectors-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>德国高端汽车制造商努力重振中国需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-premium-carmakers-struggle-revive-demand-china-2024-04-10/</link><description>德国高端汽车制造商周三公布的数据显示，第一季度中国销量进一步受到打击，保时捷和梅赛德斯-奔驰也陷入供应链困境。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:04:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-premium-carmakers-struggle-revive-demand-china-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：CPI守夜、加拿大决定、中国信用警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>出口民意调查显示，韩国反对党预计将在立法机构中保持多数席位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-opposition-parties-projected-retain-majority-legislature-exit-poll-2024-04-10/</link><description>由三个电视网络联合进行的出口民意调查显示，韩国主要反对党民主党及其盟友预计将在周三举行的单院、300 个席位的立法机构选举中赢得最多 197 个席位，从而保住多数席位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:11:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-opposition-parties-projected-retain-majority-legislature-exit-poll-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>拜登在白宫峰会上欢迎“全球伙伴”岸田</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-welcomes-global-partner-japans-kishida-white-house-summit-2024-04-10/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三在白宫欢迎日本首相岸田文雄，展示两国强大且不断发展的伙伴关系，重点是联合防务合作，以遏制咄咄逼人的中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-welcomes-global-partner-japans-kishida-white-house-summit-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯-奔驰第一季度销量因亚洲供应瓶颈而下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-q1-sales-drop-supply-bottlenecks-asia-2024-04-10/</link><description>德国高端汽车制造商梅赛德斯·奔驰 (Mercedes Benz) 周三表示，受亚洲供应瓶颈及其豪华车型系列转换的影响，第一季度销量下降 6%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-q1-sales-drop-supply-bottlenecks-asia-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，香港将于四月批准首个现货比特币 ETF</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hong-kong-set-approve-its-first-spot-bitcoin-etfs-april-sources-say-2024-04-10/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，现货比特币交易所交易基金可能于本月在香港推出，首批批准可能会在下周公布。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:26:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hong-kong-set-approve-its-first-spot-bitcoin-etfs-april-sources-say-2024-04-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>